FEMALE SPEAKER: Oh, I'm sorry.

00:00:29.320 --> 00:00:30.170
AUDIENCE: Maybe [INAUDIBLE].

00:00:30.170 --> 00:00:32.095
FEMALE SPEAKER: Thank you for
